ComicInfo.Title: Who Do You Think You Are?
ComicInfo.Summary: Who Do You Think You Are?: Allison decides to use Peter's equipment to carry on his work as The Sphinx. After screwing up during a police car chase, she questions if she should continue, but Janey tells her Peter wouldn't have left her his costume if he didn't think she was capable. When a fire traps a little girl in a burning building, she goes to help, even though the fire chief doesn't appreciate her help-- at first.
